pr_body:
This PR adds back the `--url_prefix` option. It modifies the routes to include the URL prefix, so a proper nginx config would look simply like:

```nginx
server {
    # ...
    location /flower/ {
        # no "rewrite /flower/(.*) /$1 break;" line
        proxy_pass http://localhost:5555;
    }
}
```

And run flower with:

```bash
flower --url_prefix=/flower/
```

By returning the possible generator the load_extension
can be awaited and thus await the possible generator;
this allows for the setup function to be asynchronous.

* Fixes #562;
* Fixes #567;

@schmmd Please review.

Please review my latest changes. I'm intrigued about the usage of:

PyErr_Fetch(&type, &value, &traceback);
...
PyErr_Restore(type, value, traceback);

What's exactly your intention with that?

Driver for Minicircuits USB-4SPDT-A18 RF switch box. Possibly easily adaptable to other models of USB switch boxes from Minicircuits.

Requires the Pythonnet package to load the .dll file. Also every time I have moved to a new computer I have to manually unblock the .dll file in Windows to load the file into python.

@Dominik-Vogel I made a few changes to the original version fixing some bugs with the use of addresses.
